{"tid":2509010,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇「哥斯拉大戰金剛」 ， 睇到成場係到講：「香港Mola Mola ， 香港Mola Mola」 ？","createTime":"2021-04-29T07:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:16:52.000Z","uid":42246,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e7c26fdae21551569c5ac9c170ae583b9f8d1b6","tid":2509010,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"早幾日老闆唔係到 lunch唔食飯 入左場睇<br />\n「哥斯拉大戰金剛」<br />\n<br />\n一開始都冇咩野 都係兩隻黑色怪獸（黑暴）<br />\n打來打去 打來打去<br />\n<br />\n但去到後邊真係不得了<br />\n<br />\n打打下冇啦啦引隻黑暴怪獸去香港<br />\n第一次發覺藍絲講得岩<br />\n美國真係搞亂香港<br />\n<br />\n當兩隻大怪獸（黑暴）係維港打交個陣<br />\n我情緒真係去到極點<br />\n基於本人真係「我好撚鐘意香港」<br />\n打到我屋企爛曬 著曬火 塊地爛曬<br />\n<br />\n我情不自禁係戲院大聲喊住講<br />\n「香港mola mola 香港mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n兩個黑暴大約夜晚12點打到朝早7/8點<br />\n<br />\n電影時間打足半個鐘 我就講足半個鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後坐我後幾行既呀伯 一野扔個水樽埋來<br />\n大聲屌我「收聲啦死左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n我就收左聲...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但睇完我有兩個得著<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港工程界上至下 下至上 都好堅料 d大廈好多打極唔爛，全賴我地香港工程師同地盤師傅 007 365<br />\n不眠不休建設香港，兩隻黑暴打左半日 ifc hsbc 依然屹立不倒 最後其中一隻黑暴重要背靠我地hsbc 先死唔去<br />\n<br />\n所以我係到宣布 香港工程 世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.香港真係好多黎生 好鐘意返工<br />\n兩隻黑暴打撚左半日 打極條街都有人<br />\n夜晚開始打 重有人可以飲著紅酒食花生<br />\n真勇武<br />\n朝早重打緊 條街重有人係到行來行去<br />\n打左幾個鐘都未離開到甲級寫字樓既區域<br />\n除左佢地趕住返工 我諗唔到其他原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同堆個導演一定係黃絲來<br />\n佢鏡頭下既警察勁廢<br />\n最後有個鏡頭影住個警察係企最後 推市民去擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba8788dfab030e14b3b2ab4e6560eeeaa84e3e5","tid":2509010,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcaf930808fa9dc59287650ca9c57ea911c4de35","tid":2509010,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"「香港mola mola 香港mola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"ea4471de9c7466e768413ab14a82ba1b8f6855f4","tid":2509010,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4192734c7863e1c0270cd3e8fa1e3eedd3f737bd","tid":2509010,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/Qes35FP.gif&amp;h=019cc818&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://i.makeagif.com/media/4-27-2021/k6Y9BM.gif&amp;h=ffefe19b&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"f8545a2451e952227f73bddba572265b83ee9d2a","tid":2509010,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4192734c7863e1c0270cd3e8fa1e3eedd3f737bd","tid":2509010,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/Qes35FP.gif&amp;h=019cc818&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://i.makeagif.com/media/4-27-2021/k6Y9BM.gif&amp;h=ffefe19b&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"依到寫得幾搞笑<br />\n平時d電影一定係個黑客好撚勁 最後一秒解到鎖<br />\n佢地就係到撞